{"tid":718841,"cid":17,"subCid":0,"title":"[jj插冰]護照唔同樣","createTime":"2018-06-27T04:13:26.000Z","updateTime":"2018-06-27T11:09:48.000Z","uid":63468,"like":2,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"40996cca2471907e9d33ed1de11bc117530c863e","tid":718841,"uid":63468,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-27T04:13:26.000Z","msg":"是咁的，<br />\n宜家本護照係14年整落，<br />\n咁我係16年就減咗肥40kg，<br />\n所以護照個樣同宜家有好大出入。<br />\n<br />\n上個月去泰國個陣都俾人問三問四，<br />\n話我完全唔同樣，<br />\n就連我去中國用回鄉證個陣直情俾人叫我拎埋身分證出嚟對樣(身分證同回鄉證都係未減肥整落)<br />\n<br />\n想問下嚟緊我7月16會去英國同德國，<br />\n驚俾人拒絕入境，<br />\n本護照係咪再整過會好啲?<br />\n同埋因為book機票個陣係用宜家個護照number，<br />\n到時check in係咪新舊護照俾哂個地勤就得?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ce56310b9f987399c24fb5eed195d0c3d3ec56ca","tid":718841,"uid":129039,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-27T04:19:35.000Z","msg":"而家先整驚唔驚整唔切<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8b30446ae7f18af7b09d729ed3ef9bb3b4684c25","tid":718841,"uid":146631,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-27T04:23:26.000Z","msg":"請問點減40kg? 真心求教<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1979c127ed3830ba929e69d11616ad91b7402cdc","tid":718841,"uid":22974,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-27T04:24:36.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"e0edf436ec86a0ad43be7a78735b160f73cf4fe1","tid":718841,"uid":48579,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-27T04:25:10.000Z","msg":"有無對比圖"},{"pid":"c444ac7a7176787d346b90a69d4d63b9c6536e2a","tid":718841,"uid":14494,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-27T04:25:43.000Z","msg":"即刻增番40k